    public class RationalFunctionFactoryMap<RE extends IRingElement<RE>>
extends java.util.Hashtable<IRingElementFactory<RE>,RationalFunctionFactory<RE>>
    Cash for instances of rational function factories. In order to obtain a factory for a rational function of a given base type use the method , RationalFunctionFactory>#get(Object) with an instance of IRingElement as argument.
    Author:
    Andreas Keilhauer (2014)
